name: Trick-or-treat
summary: Halloween festivities are in full swing as towns and cities across the globe prepare for the annual tradition. In London, locals can explore the best neighborhoods for trick-or-treating, while Chard town center will close to traffic for its Halloween event. In Coulsdon, residents can join the Trick or Treat Trail on October 31st. Des Moines, Iowa, will host trick-or-treating for the first time since 1938, marking a significant milestone. An East Yorkshire mother has organized an inclusive trick-or-treat event for children with disabilities. The White House also participated in the festivities, with President Biden accompanying trick-or-treaters. However, households are reminded of the age limit rule for trick-or-treating in the UK. The origins of Halloween, including trick-or-treating and pumpkin carving, are explored in a separate article, while another piece discusses the legality of trick-or-treating in the UK.
